subject: Australian Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: After handling Carlos Moyá in an intense straight-set match Tuesday, James Blake manhandled Alex Kuznetsov on Thursday, packing a high percentage of spectacular shots into 1 hour 21 minutes.
